      <div class="bg-[#1A1A1A] border-2 border-[#FF5E15] rounded-xl px-8 py-5 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-4 reveal-child">
        <p class="text-white font-heading font-semibold text-lg text-center md:text-left">I-65 restaurant shut down? Our emergency team is on call right now.</p>
